## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="34b58-102">将 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard> 操作与 <xref:System.Windows.EventTrigger> 或 <xref:System.Windows.Trigger> 一起使用以交互方式停止某个 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="34b58-102">Use a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard> action with an <xref:System.Windows.EventTrigger> or <xref:System.Windows.Trigger> to interactively stop a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="34b58-103"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard> 仅影响处于活动状态的 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> （在 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> 启动后）。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="34b58-103"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard> only affects a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> when it is active (after the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> starts).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="34b58-104">停止 storyboard 会触发 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.CurrentGlobalSpeedInvalidated> 和 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.CurrentStateInvalidated> 事件，但不会触发 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.Completed> 事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="34b58-104">Stopping a storyboard triggers the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.CurrentGlobalSpeedInvalidated> and <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.CurrentStateInvalidated> events, but not the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.Completed> event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="34b58-105"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> 不直接引用 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="34b58-105"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> does not reference a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard> directly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="34b58-106">相反，<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> 必须引用控制 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>的 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> 的 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="34b58-106">Rather, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard> must reference the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> of the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> that controls the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="34b58-107">有关示例，请参阅[如何：使用事件触发器来控制演示图板](~/docs/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-use-event-triggers-to-control-a-storyboard-after-it-starts.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="34b58-107">See [How to: Use Event Triggers to Control a Storyboard After It Starts](~/docs/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-use-event-triggers-to-control-a-storyboard-after-it-starts.md) for an example.</span></span>  
  
## <a name="pause-resume-stop-or-otherwise-control-a-storyboard-interactively"></a><span data-ttu-id="34b58-108">以交互方式暂停、继续、停止或以其他方式控制情节提要</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="34b58-108">Pause, Resume, Stop, or Otherwise Control a Storyboard Interactively</span></span>  
 <span data-ttu-id="34b58-109">为了能够以交互方式暂停、恢复或以交互方式控制 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Storyboard%2A>，请设置其 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> 的 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> 属性，并使用 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ControllableStoryboardAction> 对象（例如 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard>、<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ResumeStoryboard>或 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard>）通过引用其 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A>来控制它。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="34b58-109">To be able to pause, resume, or otherwise control a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Storyboard%2A> interactively, set the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> property of its <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> and use a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ControllableStoryboardAction> object (such as <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ResumeStoryboard>, or <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard>) to control it by referencing its <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="34b58-110">如果未指定 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> 的 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A>，则在开始后无法以交互方式控制 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Storyboard%2A>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="34b58-110">If the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> of <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> is unspecified, the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Storyboard%2A> cannot be interactively controlled after it is begun.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="34b58-111">有关详细信息，请参阅[如何：在演示图板启动后使用事件触发器控制情节提要](~/docs/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-use-event-triggers-to-control-a-storyboard-after-it-starts.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="34b58-111">See [How to: Use Event Triggers to Control a Storyboard After It Starts](~/docs/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-use-event-triggers-to-control-a-storyboard-after-it-starts.md) for more information.</span></span>  
  
